        "description": "After removing certain non ARM CPU flags to fix another issue(#7422) install fails without clear error. Since pyarrow package in the pip has configuration errors, building from the source is the only option but the installation fails due to several issues, this being one of them.\r\n\r\n*Arrow CPP build and install has been successful.*\r\n\r\n*Pyarrow build successful according to the\u00a0[guide|https://github.com/apache/arrow/blob/master/docs/source/developers/python.rst]\u00a0available here.*\r\n\r\n*But installation fails after successful build during,*\r\n\r\n{{sudo python3 setup.py install}}\r\n\r\n{{Complete logs in the external issue URL.}}",
